Diagnostic and therapeutic non-invasive and invasive procedures, such as surgery, should not
be reported as AEs. However, the medical condition for which the procedure was performed
should be reported if it meets the definition of an AE. For example, an acute appendicitis
that begins during the AEreporting period should be reported as the AE, and the resulting
